ft person when she's allowed to express herself. Hina is always busy with work and considers her tasks bothersome and exhausting</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_21d129d0-9156-4c2d-999b-4eda3dbf3c92.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5bb938d7-9336-4346-978e-4c97dc012272_character-sorasaki-hina\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_9ab62761-69f9-4dd7-b2ed-06ffb4714253.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/13946c93-0e6e-4474-bb53-5b419e2832a3_character-sorasaki-hina\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_f486ad65-445f-4a37-8f5c-cb91a232241a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/03dd8237-e508-424b-b1ed-f3cf1cd90f8b_character-hina-terror\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_619bd258-3e27-4953-a498-196501caed96.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_1da2aaeb-6f53-4e43-8e96-98d789f2d67e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><strong>Clubmates</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ff40f4bc-ab13-401b-be69-fad1a126bfd5_character-amau-ako\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4